[SHORT DESC]
Prevents confusion.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>The wielder cannot be confused. If the wielder is confused, it is instantly cured of confusion.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Confusion-inducing moves are very rare in the competitive scene, with <a href="/bw/moves/dynamicpunch">DynamicPunch</a> <a href="/bw/pokemon/machamp">Machamp</a> being the only notable user, making this ability more or less worthless. To seal the nail in its coffin, every Pokemon with access to it has much better options: <a href="/bw/pokemon/slowbro">Slowbro</a> and <a href="/bw/pokemon/slowking">Slowking</a> have <a href="/bw/abilities/regenerator">Regenerator</a>, <a href="/bw/pokemon/ludicolo">Ludicolo</a> has <a href="/bw/abilities/rain_dish">Rain Dish</a> and <a href="/bw/abilities/swift_swim">Swift Swim</a>, <a href="/bw/pokemon/grumpig">Grumpig</a> can use <a href="/bw/abilities/thick_fat">Thick Fat</a>, and <a href="/bw/pokemon/lilligant">Lilligant</a> has <a href="/bw/abilities/chlorophyll">Chlorophyll</a>.</p>